## Hints for Future Agents
- To restore a 40% threshold on a 1M-window model, set
  CLAUDE_CODE_AUTO_COMPACT_WINDOW=400000 (single var; PCT override then
  unnecessary). Caveats: threshold decouples from status line
  used_percentage, and the window applies to subagents too.
- autoCompactEnabled: true in settings is unrelated — it only toggles whether
  auto-compact runs at all (env counterpart: DISABLE_AUTO_COMPACT).
- Commit f6bcde9 "restore autocompact override at 40%" is the counterpart
  this commit reverts, for different reasons than whatever removed it before.

